author: Matthew Impelli
title: Australia and Britain Call for Investigations Into China's Handling of Coronavirus Outbreak as Multiple Countries Criticize Response
description: "The issues around the coronavirus are issues for independent review, and I think it's very important we do that," Australia's prime minister said.
content:
A number of countries have criticized China, where the coronavirus pandemic originated, for its handling of the outbreak.
